        </svg>
      </a> 
      <div class="self-center">
        <p><strong class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-black">Marcel Appelman</strong></p>
        <p class="sm:inline-block hidden max-w-sm text-gray-900">Tall, skinny Dutch guy with a penchant for cycling,
          skateboarding, and nerdy computer crap.</p>
        <p class="sm:hidden">⬆️ 🇳🇱 👨‍🦲 🧡 🚴‍♂️ 🛹 🤓 🖥 💩</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="md:max-w-3xl md:my-16 max-w-lg p-4 mx-auto my-6" id="main-content">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </main>
  <footer class="md:mb-16 mb-8">
    <ul class="flex justify-around max-w-lg p-2 mx-auto font-sans">
      <li><a class="hover:text-black text-blue-800" href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a class="hover:text-black text-blue-800" rel="external" href="https://twitter.com/huphtur">Twitter</a></li>
      <li><a class="hover:text-black text-blue-800" rel="external"
          href="https://www.instagram.com/huphtur/">Instagram</a></li>
      <li><a class="hover:text-black text-blue-800" rel="external" href="https://github.com/huphtur">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a class="hover:text-black text-blue-800" rel="external"
          href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/huphtur">Strava</a></li>
    </ul>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>